{"tid":795861,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"巴菲特度假屋劈價近30%放售　有乜啟示？","createTime":"2018-08-27T10:34:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T23:04:33.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"4b5b793369a6a2bdd2cd2d212350106b38358a30","tid":795861,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T10:34:21.000Z","msg":"股神巴菲特位於加州拉古納比奇灘(Laguna Beach)度假屋的放盤價，由2017年最初的1,100萬美元，大削約28%至790萬美元(約6,162萬港元)，他持有該物業逾40年，當年買入價僅15萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n巴菲特去年於訪問中透露，買入該海邊大宅的原因是已故妻子喜歡，但自她在2004年去世後已很少居住。巴菲特又憶述當年聖誕節假期間，躲在該宅的主人房埋手為其投資旗艦巴郡撰寫年報，亦會與子女到迪士尼樂園遊玩。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180825/bkn-20180825152417890-0825_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180825%2Fbkn-20180825152417890-0825_00842_001.html&d=I66tyhv8hYSEu0MnffRZ87%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=ca04a406\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180825/bkn-20180825152417890-0825_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n樓市即將爆煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea5f6b58a228eb50f2a01b002133f350e1283a0","tid":795861,"uid":65770,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T10:38:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lc3ttVT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Flc3ttVT.jpg&h=8ddc62bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d7b544a2138cb52a4c7807d0b83bcb4bcfeea6f","tid":795861,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T10:39:33.000Z","msg":"廢淡！<br />\n<br />\n記得月尾交租呀！"},{"pid":"0958a4244f2dff84cfef97c33ddf08ccaef18a38","tid":795861,"uid":117786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T10:54:05.000Z","msg":"條廢淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447cb2b063488b0a58345489fbf4f3b932020114","tid":795861,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08